---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Exhibitions - Digital Art Shows & Installations" description="View current and past exhibitions featuring digital artworks that explore the intersection of financial markets, generative algorithms, and visual expression.">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="exhibitions-header">
      <h1>Exhibitions</h1>
      <p class="exhibitions-subtitle">
        Digital art installations and exhibitions exploring the visual language of financial markets, algorithmic beauty, and data-driven creativity.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="current-exhibitions">
      <h2>Current & Upcoming</h2>
      <div class="exhibitions-grid">
        <article class="exhibition-card featured">
          <div class="exhibition-image">
            <div class="placeholder-image live">Live Installation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="exhibition-content">
            <div class="exhibition-meta">
              <span class="exhibition-status current">Live Now</span>
              <span class="exhibition-type">Digital Installation</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="exhibition-title">
              <a href="/art/market-emotions-live">Market Emotions: Real-Time Visualization</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="exhibition-description">
              An ongoing digital installation where market volatility data transforms into organic, breathing color fields. The VIX fear index drives algorithmic generation of visual emotions.
            </p>
            <div class="exhibition-details">
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Medium</span>
                <span class="detail-value">WebGL, Real-time Data</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Duration</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Continuous</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Digital Gallery</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/art/market-emotions-live" class="view-exhibition">Experience Live →</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="upcoming-exhibitions">
      <h2>In Development</h2>
      <div class="exhibitions-grid">
        <article class="exhibition-card">
          <div class="exhibition-image">
            <div class="placeholder-image development">In Development</div>
          </div>
          <div class="exhibition-content">
            <div class="exhibition-meta">
              <span class="exhibition-status upcoming">Coming Soon</span>
              <span class="exhibition-type">Interactive Series</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="exhibition-title">Portfolio Landscapes</h3>
            <p class="exhibition-description">
              An interactive exploration of Modern Portfolio Theory visualized as three-dimensional landscapes, where correlation becomes terrain and risk transforms into topography.
            </p>
            <div class="exhibition-details">
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Medium</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Three.js, Financial APIs</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Expected</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Q2 2024</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="exhibition-card">
          <div class="exhibition-image">
            <div class="placeholder-image concept">Concept Phase</div>
          </div>
          <div class="exhibition-content">
            <div class="exhibition-meta">
              <span class="exhibition-status concept">Concept</span>
              <span class="exhibition-type">Generative Series</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="exhibition-title">Compound Beauty</h3>
            <p class="exhibition-description">
              A generative art series where compound interest formulas drive L-system algorithms to create organic growth patterns that mirror both financial and botanical evolution.
            </p>
            <div class="exhibition-details">
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Medium</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Algorithmic Generation</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="detail-label">Research Phase</span>
                <span class="detail-value">Active</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="exhibition-philosophy">
      <div class="philosophy-content">
        <h2>Exhibition Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          These digital exhibitions explore the aesthetic dimension of financial systems—revealing the hidden beauty 
          within market psychology, the organic patterns in economic data, and the visual poetry of algorithmic trading.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each installation serves as both art and analysis, inviting viewers to experience markets not just as 
          numbers but as living, breathing ecosystems of human emotion and mathematical precision.
        </p>
        <div class="philosophy-highlights">
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3>Real-Time Data</h3>
            <p>Live market feeds transform into visual experiences as they happen</p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3>Interactive Exploration</h3>
            <p>Viewers become participants in financial market dynamics</p>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight">
            <h3>Algorithmic Beauty</h3>
            <p>Mathematical formulas reveal unexpected aesthetic dimensions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="exhibitions-sidebar">
      <div class="visit-info">
        <h3>Visit Information</h3>
        <p>All digital exhibitions are accessible 24/7 through this website. Interactive installations work best on desktop browsers with WebGL support.</p>
        
        <div class="technical-requirements">
          <h4>Technical Requirements</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari)</li>
            <li>WebGL support for 3D installations</li>
            <li>Stable internet connection for real-time data</li>
            <li>Desktop recommended for full experience</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="newsletter-prompt">
          <h4>Stay Updated</h4>
          <p>Get notified when new exhibitions launch or installations update.</p>
          <a href="/subscribe" class="subscribe-link">Subscribe to Updates</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .exhibitions-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .exhibitions-header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 120px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent-primary), transparent);
  }
  
  .exhibitions-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .current-exhibitions,
  .upcoming-exhibitions {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .exhibitions-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .exhibition-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .exhibition-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
  }
  
  .exhibition-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }
  
  .exhibition-image {
    height: 200px;
    background: var(--bg-accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image.live {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a52);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image.development {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4ecdc4, #44a08d);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  .placeholder-image.concept {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #a8a8a8, #999999);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; }
  }
  
  .exhibition-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  
  .exhibition-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .exhibition-status {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  
  .exhibition-status.current {
    background: #10bf7a;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .exhibition-status.upcoming {
    background: #1677be;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .exhibition-status.concept {
    background: var(--text-muted);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .exhibition-type {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .exhibition-title {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Text', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  
  .exhibition-title a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .exhibition-title a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .exhibition-description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .exhibition-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .detail-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .detail-label {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  
  .detail-value {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  
  .view-exhibition {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .view-exhibition:hover {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
    transform: translateX(4px);
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .exhibition-philosophy {
    background: var(--blog-parchment);
    padding: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .philosophy-content h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Text', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  
  .philosophy-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .philosophy-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .highlight h3 {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .highlight p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .exhibitions-sidebar {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .visit-info {
    background: var(--bg-accent);
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .visit-info h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Text', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }
  
  .visit-info p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .technical-requirements h4,
  .newsletter-prompt h4 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .technical-requirements ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .technical-requirements li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .newsletter-prompt {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  
  .newsletter-prompt p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .subscribe-link {
    background: var(--accent-primary);
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .subscribe-link:hover {
    background: var(--accent-secondary);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .exhibitions-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .exhibition-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .philosophy-highlights {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .exhibition-philosophy {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .exhibition-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>